          </em><em>without prior notice for any reason deemed  appropriate by CDS staff, including, <br>
          but not limited to, the emergence of a  conflict with a library- or course-related event. </em><p></p>
          </li>
        </ul>
        </li>
      </ul>
  </li>
            <li>The maximum capacity of the rooms may not be exceeded due to safety  regulations.</li>
          </ul>
